								src={cnnInterviewImage} 
								alt="John Engates live on CNN discussing Healthcare.gov" 
								class="tv-screenshot clickable"
								width={800}
								height={450}
								format="webp"
								quality={90}
							/>
						</a>
						<p class="image-caption">Live on CNN providing expert analysis on the Healthcare.gov recovery efforts</p>
					</div>
					<div class="media-coverage-list">
						<h4>Featured Coverage:</h4>
						<ul class="coverage-items">
							<li><strong>CNN</strong> - Live television interview and analysis on contractor management for the recovery effort</li>
							<li><strong>PBS NewsHour</strong> - Expert commentary on potential complications and technical architecture solutions
								<br><a href="https://www.pbs.org/newshour/show/will-there-be-more-complications-to-the-health-care-website" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="media-link">View Interview →</a>
							</li>
							<li><strong>CBS News</strong> - Insights on preventing traffic jams and scaling government IT infrastructure
								<br><a href="https://www.cbsnews.com/news/white-house-woos-healthcaregov-critic-with-private-briefing/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="media-link">White House Briefing Coverage →</a>
							</li>
							<li><strong>NPR (National Public Radio)</strong> - Analysis of the "tech surge" strategy and infrastructure fixes
								<br><a href="https://www.npr.org/sections/alltechconsidered/2013/12/01/248078217/the-key-test-for-healthcare-gov-is-the-part-you-cant-see" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="media-link">Key Test Analysis →</a> | <a href="https://www.npr.org/sections/alltechconsidered/2013/10/22/239220962/the-healthcare-gov-tech-surge-is-racing-against-the-clock" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="media-link">Tech Surge Coverage →</a>
							</li>
							<li><strong>USA Today</strong> - Quoted on the need for complete infrastructure overhaul
								<br><a href="https://www.usatoday.com/story/news/politics/2013/11/27/tech-experts-health-care-site/3771901/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="media-link">Tech Experts Analysis →</a>
							</li>
							<li><strong>InformationWeek</strong> - In-depth technical analysis of the recovery efforts
