							<li><strong>Fox 13 News</strong> - Compared website recovery to "rocket launch" requiring precision coordination</li>
							<li><strong>Louisville Courier-Journal</strong> - Advocated for total system overhaul rather than incremental fixes</li>
							<li><strong>Open Health News</strong> - Series of articles on healthcare IT transformation</li>
