		<!-- 2012 -->
		<div class="year-section">
			<h3 class="year-header">2012</h3>
			<div class="appearances-grid">
				<article class="appearance-card highlight special">
					<h3>LSI Accelerating Innovation Summit (AIS) 2012</h3>
					<p class="appearance-context">San Jose, California • November 13, 2012</p>
					<p>Main speaker at LSI's fifth annual summit, presenting on "Rethinking Future Storage Strategies" to industry leaders grappling with the data explosion. Addressed how the industry should reshape storage architectures in the era of cloud computing, drawing on experience building OpenStack Swift and scaling Rackspace's infrastructure to support the world's largest digital properties.</p>
					<div class="appearance-image">
						<a href={ais2012Image.src} target="_blank">
							<Image 
								src={ais2012Image} 
