					<h3>ISSA International Conference</h3>
					<p class="appearance-context">Keynote Speaker • Security Leadership</p>
					<p>Featured speaker at the Information Systems Security Association conference, discussing the convergence of AI and cybersecurity, and how organizations can prepare for emerging threats.</p>
